briefdescription.para: A minimal YAML parser supporting the subset needed for mapping specs.

detaileddescription.para:
Supports:
Scalars (strings, numbers, booleans)
Maps (key: value)
Lists (- item)
Inline maps ({ key: value })
Inline lists ([ item, item ])
Comments (# comment)
Multi-line strings (basic support)

Does NOT support:
Anchors and aliases
Tags
Complex multi-line strings (|, >)
Multiple documents
